channel.title: Can't login in again on account when logged out? [PI]
channel.description:
Hello,
I am using the source Deathlypvpz. I added a quest without any compiling errors. I changed the client ip. And compiled without any errors.
Now if i open my client. I login on an random account. And i logout again. And i try to set my playerrights to 3. And i log in again. I can't login and get this error in my source.
